      "description": "Affordable and functional daily driver looking for a new home! This vehicle runs and drives, making it a solid option for budget-conscious buyers who need reliable transportation. It does show its age \u2014 expect visible wear on the interior and exterior, and it may benefit from some attention and TLC along the way. Priced honestly to reflect its current condition, this is a great opportunity to get behind the wheel without breaking the bank!",
