    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Real Talk \u2014 Affordable Wheels for the Budget-Conscious Buyer!** We're not here to sugarcoat it \u2014 this vehicle is showing its age with noticeable wear and some mechanical issues that need attention. But hey, that's exactly why the price is so friendly! Whether you're a DIY mechanic looking for a project, need a basic point-A-to-point-B runner, or just want to stretch every dollar, this could be your ticket. Come take a look \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects it honestly! \ud83d\udd27",
