      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Pristine & Showroom-Fresh \u2014 A True Mint Condition Gem! This car is the real deal \u2014 an exceptionally well-preserved vehicle that turns heads and delivers an outstanding driving experience! The exterior gleams with flawless paint and zero visible blemishes, while the interior looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Mechanically, it's in top-notch shape \u2014 everything works exactly as it should, with no issues to report. If you've been searching for a vehicle you can be genuinely proud of, this is it. Opportunities like this don't come around often \u2014 come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $4,500, a price that honestly reflects its poor condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that means before you consider purchasing. This car has significant wear and mechanical issues that should be expected at this price point. The body shows considerable rust, dents, and paint deterioration. The engine runs but is not reliable, with known issues including rough idling and occasional stalling. The interior is heavily worn, with torn upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and non-functional electronics. Brakes and suspension components are due for immediate attention and should be inspected by a qualified mechanic before driving. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project car, someone seeking parts, or a mechanically experienced individual who understands the investment of time and money required to bring it to roadworthy condition. We strongly recommend a pre-purchase inspection. No warranty is implied or offered.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a well-maintained, dependable car that has been carefully looked after and is ready for daily use. The exterior presents nicely overall, with the paint retaining a reasonable shine and only minor surface blemishes consistent with normal use over time. There are no significant dents or rust concerns, and the body panels align properly. The interior is clean and functional, with seating surfaces showing light wear but no major tears or damage. All primary controls, electronics, and comfort features are in working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and reliably, and routine maintenance has been kept up to date. The tires have adequate tread remaining, and the brakes are in serviceable condition. This is a solid, honest vehicle that a buyer can depend on without needing to invest in major repairs right away.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition \u2014 best suited for buyers on a tight budget who are comfortable with a project car or need basic transportation and can handle ongoing repairs. The car does start and can be driven, but it shows significant wear throughout. The exterior has noticeable rust, dents, and faded paint. The interior is worn with tears in the upholstery and some non-functioning features. Mechanically, it runs but will require attention \u2014 expect to invest in repairs to keep it reliably on the road. This is priced to reflect its condition honestly, and we encourage any serious buyer to inspect it thoroughly before purchase.",
      "price": 4500.0,
